N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 226.8 - Fees

State Regulations

There shall be no fee charged for: (a) inspection of records; (b) search for records; (c) any certification pursuant to this Part; or
(d) copies of records. Notes
